The Enterprise Capital Management Technology (ECMT) team within Finance Technology consists of high performing individuals who collaborate with Enterprise Capital Management in Treasury to deliver technology solutions that calculate key Capital measures such as Risk-Weighted Assets, Loss Given Default and Exposure at Default, allowing for efficient and prudent management of Capital at the total bank level as well as for critical legal entities and reporting to lines of business. 
