The ECMT team supports a large-scale application which offer software engineers multiple pathways for growth. Moving vertically within the SDM Software Engineering family of roles, across technology components or business facing domains. Horizontal movement to other role families such as Delivery or Architecture is also supported. Team members are encouraged to seek out new opportunities within the team. 
